---
title: Middle Eastern Spiced Chicken with Almond Rice, Roasted Sweet Potato and Garlic-Lemon Yogurt Sauce
description: The star of this dish is the Middle Eastern spiced chicken. Drizzled with a garlic-lemon yogurt sauce and served alongside fragrant almond rice.
